    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Click and Conquer》是一款轻松、短时的增量体验游戏。在隐藏敌人的网格上投掷炸弹，利用获得的奖励增强你的实力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向隐藏的敌人投掷炸弹以赚取货币。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/9ddc96853976e67e84cee74759a5c0b6.poster.avif?t=1770778769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/9ddc96853976e67e84cee74759a5c0b6.webm?t=1770778769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/9ddc96853976e67e84cee74759a5c0b6.mp4?t=1770778769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用货币提升被动收入、增强炸弹威力并解锁新地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/0b175d96ac2cbe497ebf48c91732a5c0.poster.avif?t=1770778769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/0b175d96ac2cbe497ebf48c91732a5c0.webm?t=1770778769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/0b175d96ac2cbe497ebf48c91732a5c0.mp4?t=1770778769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着轰炸战役的扩大，探索超过12张规模和奖励不断提升的地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/f89f2b555fd74b908aa13f78c6842749.poster.avif?t=1770778769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/f89f2b555fd74b908aa13f78c6842749.webm?t=1770778769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/f89f2b555fd74b908aa13f78c6842749.mp4?t=1770778769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过重置进度进行声望转换，以换取强力且永久的升级——包括毁灭性的核弹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/1b9de11ff8f201d1b32c00db69d24483.poster.avif?t=1770778769\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/1b9de11ff8f201d1b32c00db69d24483.webm?t=1770778769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267900/extras/1b9de11ff8f201d1b32c00db69d24483.mp4?t=1770778769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >满足感十足的增量式成长。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松、短时的游戏体验（约2~4小时可通关）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两棵技能树，可提升能力与经济发展。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过12张地图可供解锁与升级。</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 法语, 意大利语, 保加利亚语, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 泰语, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语",
